//   Portions © Paul Hammant — Tsyne port; AeVG (Aether) port, 2026
//
// Because the squarified-treemap design, the colour-by-size/depth/type scheme,
// and the 3D-bevel rendering are carried over from GrandPerspective, this file
// inherits its copyleft: it is distributed under the GPL-2.0 (or, at your
